How to Bootstrap EC2 Instance with user data script in Terraform | Terraform 'userdata' examples


Refer this official Documentation by Terraform on Userdata:
https://registry.terraform.io/providers/serverscom/serverscom/latest/docs/guides/user-data



Here I have added script.sh inside ec2.tf file rest all code is same as previous. Once the run the "terraform apply -auto-approve"
then copy the Public_IP and paste in the browser "http://234.0.134.145" and you will se the content on web Page. as wewritten in the user-data.
